# Generated preview files — DON'T exclude them.
# They are regenerated during the Docker build (see Dockerfile builder stage)
# and required at runtime by the hover-preview modal at
# `/template-previews/preview-:slug.html`. If excluded, every preview returns
# the "Preview not yet generated" placeholder in production.
# templates/preview-*.html
